    <h1>Constellation Energy (CEG)<br/>Intrinsic Value</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">A transparent, two-stage discounted cash flow valuation of Constellation Energy — using FY2025 actuals, disclosed assumptions, and one final number.</p>
    <p class="date">Updated March 18, 2026 · Data: FY2025 Financials</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <!-- ═══ THE VERDICT ═══ -->
